en.desc: Demongrub Pits is an underground Jumping Puzzle located in southeast Queensdale.

en.title: Grendich Gamble
en.desc: Grendich Gamble is a jumping puzzle in the west part of the Diessa Plateau It is located on a building next to a Skillpoint with Cannons and Trebuchets as well as Ascalonian Ghosts on it.

en.title: Loreclaw Expanse
en.desc: The Loreclaw Expanse is the southeastern section of the Plains of Ashford and includes the seperatist camp in the area.

en.title: The Collapsed Observatory
en.desc: The Collapsed Observatory is a jumping puzzle in the southeast part of Kessex Hills. The entrance is straight south of Cereboth Canyon and the cave eventually leads to Isgarren's View.
